<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Action Required: Customer Ticket Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #008000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #008000;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #008000;
        }
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Action Required: Customer Ticket Update</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p><strong>Ticket Number:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= @ticket_number %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Date Created:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= @ticket_created_at %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Customer Email:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= @customer_email %></span></p>
            <p><strong>Issue Summary:</strong> <span class="highlight"><%= @issue_description %></span></p>

            <p>Hello <strong><%= @service_provider_name %></strong>,</p>
            <p>
                You have been assigned a new customer issue to resolve. Please review the details above and take the necessary actions 
                to address the issue promptly. Ensure that the ticket status is updated accordingly to keep the customer informed.
            </p>
            <p>
                For more information or to update the ticket, please log into your service dashboard using the button below.
            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= @tracking_url %>" class="button">Access Ticket Details</a>
            </div>
            <p>
                If you have any questions or need additional details, please reach out to our support team using the contact 
                information below. We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter.
            </p>
            <p>Thank you,</p> 
            <p>The <span class="highlight"><%= @company_name %></span> Team</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                Contact us at: <a href="mailto:<%= @customer_support_email %>"><%= @customer_support_email %></a> 
                | <a href="tel:<%= @customer_support_phone_number %>"><%= @customer_support_phone_number %></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> <%= @company_name %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
